Class Candidate

  • java.lang.Object
    • Candidate
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Comparable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    RegisteredCandidate, WriteInCandidate

    public abstract class Candidate
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Comparable
    Created by Rakshith on 4/6/2017. This class is responsible for having common characteristics for candidates. This is made abstract in order to allow this to be used by the CandidateFactory class. Implements cloneable and comparable to allow cloning and comparing mechanisms to be done.
